# File Ownership Enforcer

## Purpose
Prevent overlapping writes by multiple agents to the same path/glob.

## Inputs
- `docs/plans/file-assignments.json`

## Behavior
- Deny concurrent/overlapping writes; surface owner and readers.
- Propose remediation: reassign or split globs; record changes.

